title: FA Cup - 4th Round - Highlights and Review show - 26 Jan 2013
description:
Show length 1 Hour 30 Minutes. Highlights length 1 hour. 

Matt Smith is joined by Gordon Strachan and Clarke Carlisle to present action from the opening fourth-round fixtures, including Macclesfield Town v Wigan Athletic, Stoke City v Manchester City and Norwich City v Luton Town. Places in the last 16 were at stake, and Conference Premier side Macclesfield were looking to cause another shock at Moss Rose, having defeated Championship high-fliers Cardiff City there in round three. With commentary by Clive Tyldesley and Andy Townsend, and reports from Ned Boultin

Matches covered :

Stoke City v Manchester City 	


	Macclesfield Town v Wigan Athletic 	


	Derby County v Blackburn Rovers 	


	Brighton and Hove Albion v Arsenal 	


	Hull City v Barnsley 	


	Norwich City v Luton Town 	


	Middlesbrough v Aldershot Town 	


	Queens Park Rangers v Milton Keynes Dons FC 	


	Reading 4 - 0 Sheffield United 	


	Huddersfield Town v Leicester City 	


	Bolton Wanderers v Everton 	


	Manchester United v Fulham
